Name: Awilda
Profile:
I'm the head of the swim team, Awilda! 
I'm picked to be a top contender in the worldwide swimming competition they're planning to hold! 
At least once everything going on calms down. 
That's why I'm working my tail off day and night practicing my swimming technique!
DisLike: Things that show her reflection, Being alone
Pros: Always being positive and upbeat
Cons: Never giving anyone enough space

Name: Tayshet
Profile:
So I'm Tayshet. I'm from Eisengrad. 
I carry out whatever orders are given to me. 
But what I won't do is kill people or do anything bad. 
And I'm never going to break that promise. I'm an Eisengrad soldier after all. 
Not some little rascal anymore.
Pros: Never tells lies
Cons: Can't take people's feelings into account when speaking

Name: Kuala Lum
Profile:
I've been sheltered from the world since I was very little, so I don't know much about a lot of things! 
But I do plan on taking over the family business one day. 
That's why I studied hard on tea leaf cultivation and running a business, so I should be good!♪
CharacterSkill: Getting a stranger to relax with tea
Pros: Offering delicious tea
Cons: Doesn't move when stuck in dark, cramped spaces
Hobby: Expanding her tea collection, Tea parties

Name: Jeran
Profile:
Grrrahhhh! I'm Jeran the tiger and I've been living in the Flamarine forests! 
Right now I fall under wildlife conservation, so I've just been chopping down trees with my axe and selling them!
Pros: Kind to animals, Innocent
Cons: A bit lacking in common sense
Hobby: Walks in the jungle, Naps, Testing out her own strength

Name: Volklingen
Profile:
I used to be assigned to a remote region of Eisengrad, you know? 
They used to call me "evil bailiff..." Wait, no they respected me, you know?
Pros: Superhuman strength
Cons: Everything. She's kind to herself and harsh to others.

Name: Ohana
Profile:
I'm Ohana. I'm the dorm mom for all the students. 
My biggest joy is making delicious food for everyone to eat. 
I don't really enjoy fighting, but I might be of some help.
Pros: A huge heart that can accept anyone.
Cons: She tends to treat people too much like children

Name: Futamata
Profile:
I'm Futamata!♪ I'm an apprentice of Ooenomiya of Mount Ooe! And I'm a pop idol too! They call us the Ooe Big Four in my hometown. 
I'm good at fighting too, but I'm even better at singing and dancing!♪ 
We mainly do shows at the public hall. My dream is to have a giant crowd of my fans gather on Mount Ooe. Someone start the music!
Pros: Always smiling
Cons: Butts in whenever the conversation is about being cute

Name: Penang Hill
Profile:
I used to work at the Night Butterfly, a nightclub in Flamarine. 
I mostly danced. Oh and fought in the underground ring too. They laid me off recently though.
DisLike: Harmful insects, Water (because it gets rid of her sweat)
Pros: Able to work towards her dreams
Cons: Sweats way too much, Tends to not trust others and talk very curtly

Name: Finchley
Profile:
I'm Finchley. I am also working as an instructor at the St. Iris Knight Academy. 
They call me the "demon instructor," but I am just teaching them what is going to keep them alive. 
While I wouldn't consider myself friendly, I'm not as scary as they make me out to be.
DisLike: Drawing conclusions just based on results.
Pros: Not getting swayed by bits of information
Cons: Being able to smooth things over with her words

Name: Queensway
Profile:
I'm Queensway of the Order of St. Iris. 
I'm still a knight in training at the Academy, but I will do everything in my power to not bring dishonor to the SSS. 
As I set out tracks that have yet to be discovered!
DisLike: People that don't take things seriously
Pros: Altruistic and a sense of justice
Cons: Unable to easily work with people that have a different set of values

Name: Notting Hill
Profile:
I'm Notting Hill from the Order of St. Iris. It's an honor to be a part of the SSS. 
I'm rivals with Queensway who got into the SSS before me. 
She must be proud to know she has a rival like me. 
I'm gonna give it my all and not let her down. I swear it by my sword and my teachings as a knight.
DisLike: People that don’t put in any effort
CharacterSkill: Fencing taught to her by the Knight Academy
Pros: Keeping her word
Cons: Trying things out without knowing if she can do it

Name: Ooenomiya
Profile:
I'm the protector of Mount Ooe, Ooenomiya. I was living out the retired life on the outskirts of Nishiki. I used to help out the Nishiki army here and there. 
I can't believe the Alliance would need my help… Then again, you shouldn't concern yourself too much about me. Think about my apprentices that joined along with me. I'm here to protect them, after all.
Pros: Good caretaker
Cons: Annoying when drunk

Name: Putra
Profile:
Hiya! I'm Putra!♪ 
I'm an ocean girl, born and bred right here in Flamarine! 
I'm real good at diving without any gear, so if you drop anything be sure to give me a shout!
Pros: Never letting her smile fade
Cons: Not giving enough personal space

Name: Karakawa
Profile:
I'm another one of the Ooe Big Four, Karakawa. 
I'm not so good around…men. What if they touch me? Someone could get hurt. 
Like one of them. But you don't have to worry about any of that, sir! 
I wanna be your friend is what I mean!
CharacterSkill: A wide range of spear techniques
Pros: Able to withstand mental attacks
Cons: A bad habit of punching guys when they touch her
Hobby: Throwing her spear to ride it around in the air

Name: Alexandra
Profile:
I mash up all kinds of fruit with my weapon here. 
Helps me turn it all into juice! 
I'm getting great reviews from everyone at school and on the train even! Of course it's not free though?
DisLike: Being reprimanded, Her family home, Bugs
Pros: Her pure heart
Cons: Getting carried away

Name: Phnom Penh
Profile:
You see, I used to be top of my class back home. 
I can study, I can do housework, and I can fight just fine. Perfect partner to die together with, don't you think?
Like: Lack of oxygen, Underwater scenery, Smiles
DisLike: Floods, People that look down on other's interests
Pros: Able to take accurate measures without panicking in times of crisis
Cons: Trying to pull people underwater

Name: Fussen
Profile:
You wish to learn about me? I couldn't care less who you are. 
I'm from a royal family that has ruled over Eisengrad for ages now. 
I assume that's enough for you to know about me for now.
DisLike: Socializing with materialists, Her obligation to the commoners
CharacterSkill: Being able to control lesser monsters
Pros: Has a keen eye for the beautiful things in life
Cons: Has no interest in involving herself with people

Name: Novella
Profile:
I am Novella of the Verforet Military Police.
I'm a pharmacist, so I'm good at mixing medicines and making perfumes.
By the way, have you seen Vivienne?
There's an aphrodisiac I'd like to try ......
No, I have a perfume I'd like her to use.......
DisLike: Men that touch women too friendly
Pros: Able to get along with anyone that's a woman
Cons: The fact that she touches women too much

Name: Karlsruhe
Profile:
I've technically been in the army since I was a kid, but I don't have much real battle experience. 
I was mainly doing rear support and helping coordinate court-martials. 
Put me to work, Your Excellency.♪
Pros: Never neglecting to make a plan beforehand
Cons: It takes time for her to produce results

Name: Yakutsk
Profile:
I'm Yakutsk and I'm part of the Eisengrad army. 
I come from the north where all we have is snow, ice and Mist. 
Allow me to show you how I fight proudly bearing the Eisengrad name.
Pros: A strong sense of responsibility
Cons: Being harsher than she truly means to be
Hobby: Reading picture books and adventure novels

Name: Shimoamazu
Profile:
I'm Shimoamazu, first apprentice of Ooenomiya, second of my name. 
They call us the Ooe Big Four, but we're not that special. 
I'm Amanohashidate's caregiver. No more, no less.
Pros: Unwavering, Unphased by lonliness and darkness
Cons: Unable to put much emotion into her words

Name: Amanohashidate
Profile:
They call me wittle Amanohashidate! 
We're the master's apprentices, so that's why they call us the Ooe Big Four. 
Our master is super strong, but real sweet. 
I just wuv her!
Like: Deer (Both to look at and to eat)
DisLike: A battalion of spellcasters still dressed in their cermonial robes
Pros: Always keeps her promises
Cons: Isn't always reasonable

Name: Orleans
Profile:
I'm Orleans. 
I'm the one that hears the voice of the Saint of the Mist. 
Also known as La Pucelle. 
I have inherited her powers and intentions to become the next Saint of the Mist. 
Everything is so that we can put a stop to all of the conflict in out world. 
Come, follow me. Let us fight for a world with hope.
Pros: Being able to interact with people without any favoritism
Cons: Too religious to vibe well with soldiers

Name: Yoshino
Profile:
Well hey there, I'm Yoshino, a tailor at Somei-Ya. 
I'm good with tinkering with machines too, but at the end of the day I'm still just a tailor. 
I'm trying to spread the word about Somei-Ya to repay the debt I owe to the happy couple that own the place.
Pros: Able to accept everyting with a positive attitude
Cons: Blurting things out without reading the room

Name: Volgo
Profile:
Name's Volgo. I belong to the sniper division of the Northern Eisengrad Army. 
I don't know what you've heard of me, but I'm by no means an elite soldier. 
I'm just good at handling a gun. 
So don't take it away from me. I'll quit if I don't have my gun to shoot. 
No changing my mind about that.
DisLike: Overly chatty people, Places without any cover
Pros: Very patient
Cons: Lacking a sense of humor, Stern expression

Name: Leipzig
Profile:
I am but a low ranking officer belonging to the Public Relations Department of the Eisengrad Central Army. 
You can also find me wearing my Sensenmann costume and doing charity work.
Pros: Always completes the task as hand without complaining
Cons: Not very accomodating

Name: Fayette
Profile:
I'm Fayette and I'm from the Order of St. Iris. 
My situation is a bit different from the other knights. 
How do I put it? 
My family have been leading the rabble outside the castle for generations now. 
Less so knights and more so soldiers. You'll see what I mean in time, I suppose.
Pros: Able to get along with anyone right away
Cons: Always thinks about what is needed and not needed to accomplish a goal

Name: Murmansk
Profile:
I have a condition where I disappear if I don't eat meat. 
That's why I learned how to use a gun…to get the meat I crave.
Pros: Able to genuinely accept anything
Cons: Always ends up seeing other people's pets as emergency rations

Name: Amiens
Profile:
I'm Amiens. 
I love exploring old ruins and sacred sites. 
Not the biggest fan of rainstorms and lightning. 
I believe that you'll be rewarded if you just don't give up, no matter how bad things get. Don't want you thinking I'm a negative Nancy now, do I?
Pros: Able to face adversity head-on
Cons: Expects to lose before things even begin

Name: Anzio
Profile:
I run the orphanage that tries to move past the racial and border issues here in Verforet! 
I'm good at taking care of kids, laundry and cooking, but nothing to do with fire!
Pros: The virtue to work for others
Cons: Extremely sensitive skin, Going into the ecstacy state

Name: Dover
Profile:
I'm Dover. I'm half elf, half St. Iris human. 
My dad is from St. Iris and my mom is an elf from Verforet. 
I had always dreamed of life in the city and tried testing into the Knight Academy. 
But my marks in composition were so bad that I flunked out... 
B-but! They saw something special in me when I shot my bow and made an exception just for me! Pretty amazing, huh?
Pros: Always cheerful
Cons: Saying she can do things there's no way she can do
Hobby: Checking out travel spots in magazines

Name: Bourse
Profile:
I'm Bourse from Verforet. 
I'm not one for bright places or lots going on. 
But I really love my Vivienne. 
So I always keep a safe distance as I watch over her.
Pros: Unswayed by other's opinions
Cons: Unable to say her opinion to someone's face

Name: Rouen
Profile:
I'm Rouen. I've been entrusted by the Holy Angel Saint-Sever. 
There are tons of Sacred Holy areas in the Verforet forest. 
You wanna try stepping into Holy territory then?
Pros: Being cheerful despite it all
Cons: When she gets ideas of grandure she tends to make some selfish decisions

Name: Lancaster
Profile:
I'm Lancaster, an apprentice Knight at the Order of St. Iris. 
I prefer my spells over a sword. 
I am hoping to breathe some new life into the St. Iris nobility and the Knights. 
Oh, I'm not so good at talking in front of people by the way. 
I usually just leave that up to Notting Hill...
DisLike: People that like saying "where there's a will, there's a way" without actually doing anything
Pros: Able to see the big picture without letting emotions get in the way
Cons: Can't do chores, no hesitate to say because she thinks she's right

Name: Vivienne
Profile:
I'm Vivienne and I was born in Verforet. 
Conductor, it's a pleasure to meet you!♪ 
Wanna hear something that shocks people the first time they meet me? 
Before I joined the SSS I used to be pretty crazy in the Verforet Military Police. I'm serious.
Pros: Her self-confidence and the fact that she's not shy about anything
Cons: Unable to resist clothes and cosmetics

Name: Salem
Profile:
I was born in the forested area of St. Iris, which is also known as… 
"The Witch Forest." 
It was there that I inherited all the knowledge and skills of the witches that have lived there for ages. 
I rushed over to be of some use to you to save this world of ours.
Like: Toads, Playing in the mud, etc.
CharacterSkill: Able to use ancient St. Iris magic
Pros: Kind to things that are normally detested
Cons: Dislikes normal girls gettigng excited over things

Name: Roswell
Profile:
We have been observing this planet before history was recorded. 
Currently this body that I inhabit called Roswell is how I am going about my investigation.
CharacterSkill: Able to do things beyong human comprehension
Pros: A wide range of knowledge and incredible mental capabilities
Cons: No common sense

Name: Acapulco
Profile:
I am a government official representing the central Flamarine government, and I work my tail off in the Underwater Temple. 
Well, I basically am just cleaning up my dumb sister's mess. It's stressing me out.
CharacterSkill: Able to somewhat control marine creatures
Pros: Has wisdom beyond her years
Cons: Foul mouthed, Tends to blurt out people's complexes

Name: Las Vegas
Profile:
So I'm a dealer at the biggest casino in St. Iris. 
Wanna place some bets? It'll be fine, whether you win or lose! 
People seem to always break even! 
You'll end up with the same amount you started with, I think!
CharacterSkill: Extreme bad luck (due to living in a place with lots of paramornal activity)
Pros: Positive and always able to recover
Cons: Extremely unlucky

Name: Abashiri
Profile:
I am the warden of Ezo Prison which is located on the northern most part of Nishiki. 
The prisoners there all fear me. They even started calling me the warden of Hell. 
At any rate, no one has been able to escape…
Pros: Excellent as a prison warden
Cons: Pessimistic and not one to be action oriented

Name: Passy
Profile:
I run all kinds of brand-name shops in my home kingdom of Verforet. 
I'm also a patron for all you art collectors out there. I just love beautiful things!♪
CharacterSkill: Finding the "best aspects" of artwork, etc.
Pros: Able to accept and love everything
Cons: Too accepting and easy fooled

Name: Tianjin
Profile:
The name's Tianjin. I am the Doc's assistant. 
And by assistant, I mean that I make all the food and protect the Doc from bad guys. 
Oh, and by the Doc, I mean Dr. Beijing who's also part of the SSS. 
Wherever you find the Doc, you'll find me too!
DisLike: People that make fun of other's upbringing or birthplace
Pros: Taking care of her teammates
Cons: Believing everything

Name: Detroit
Profile: I'm Detroit and I came from a place where there used to be a factory near the northern border. Yeah, you're right. That's where a bunch of bad guys hang out and the city doesn't have the best reputation. Though I can hold my own in fights, not to mention take out some Mist Monsters. Huh, what about it? I don't really want to talk about the past. If I feel like talking about it, I'll tell you.
CharacterSkill: Getting into arguments, Lockpicking, Making weapons
Pros: Able to face anything without being afraid
Cons: Unable to encourage people when things are hopeless

Name: Chitose
Profile:
My hometown offered me up as a sacrifice me when I was young to make their land fertile. 
No one really knows if that had triggered some sort of curse from within me… 
And now as you can see, I'm immortal, stuck at this age forever. I've become an eternal guardian that bridges the gap between the dead and the living.
CharacterSkill: Able to go between realm of the dead and the living
Pros: Kind and very helpful
Cons: Not very strong and lacking stamina

Name: Pancras
Profile:
Greetings, Conductor. I'm Pancras. 
I'm hoping to be the most elegant Train Knight in the SSS. 
I'm even making sure I take care with what I wear. These panties I have on are my favorites. 
If you wanna drop by my room sometime, I can give you a tour of my collection.
Like: Necklaces, Underwear that show off the body
Pros: Being completely confident in herself.
Cons: Trying to force her interests on other people

Name: Naypyidaw
Profile:
I'm a court mage working at the Underwater Temple, the center of government in Flamarine. 
I must point out that I studied in St. Iris, the magic capital of the world and boy, did I study hard. 
I would say I'm well versed in all basic magic.
Pros: Very skilled in magic, Kind and friendly to everyone
Cons: Doesn't value herself

Name: Puerto Rico
Profile:
I work as a government official for the Underwater Temple here in Flamarine. 
I'm one of the few that have the privilege to pass the laws around here and that's a privilege that's unrivaled. 
I'm just reading what's written here, I don't even get what I'm saying?
Like: All people and a healthy lifestyle
Pros: As merciful as a saint
Cons: Troublemaker

Name: Shibuya
Profile:
The name's Shibuya and I caused a whole lot of trouble in my hometown. 
I'm basically famous for it. 
It's gotten so bad that I get thank you notes that have threats hidden in code in them!?
DisLike: Having to wait, Things that are immoral
Pros: A quick learner, Good reflexes
Cons: A split between her self-recognition and what other's think of her

Name: Beijing
Profile:
I'm Beijing and I'm part of the Eisengrad Central Army. 
Probably better to call myself a researcher instead of a soldier. You see, I'm doing research in combining Mist Stones and their magic with things. 
Not just weapons! Everyday objects and even toys for kids. 
If you got a good idea, let me know. I'll be sure to try and make it.
Like: All types of dim sum, Manga
CharacterSkill: Able to combine machines and Mist Stones and control them
Pros: Doesn't discriminate or have a notion of prejudice
Cons: Cannot honestly say what she's thinking
Hobby: Inventing things unrelated to her work

Name: Pennsylvania
Profile:
I'm from the Order of St. Iris, call me Pennsylvania. 
Um, I was born in Verforet. I used to be part of their Military, too. 
A whole lot happened and I ended up moving to St. Iris. 
My goal and dream is to become the world's best archer. It's a pleasure to meet you.
Pros: Doesn't speak ill of others and always looks for their good qualities
Cons: Unable to consider others when the topic turns to archery

Name: Termini
Profile:
I am the vessel of an ancient alchemist's soul. 
I've been reincarnated countless times and have lived multiple lifetimes. 
You know, your basic concept of everlasting life…? But physically, I'm just your average girl.
Pros: Knowing everything
Cons: A little behind when it comes to modern things

Name: Victoria
Profile:
Conductor, it's a pleasure to meet you. I'm Victoria. I'm the maid assigned to Paddington. 
I will do my best to not bring shame to such a noble as her. 
I will warn you that I have a bad habit of saying some nasty things sometimes. 
If that ever happens, just give me a spanking.
Pros: Nerves of steel
Cons: Making a scene even out of things that can be resolved peacefully

Name: Tombstone
Profile:
Hey, I'm Tombstone! 
No one can beat me in a quick draw or trick riding on horses! 
I don't know much about complicated stuff, I'll admit. 
But you can consider my gun yours until the day I'm 6 feet under! Pew, pew, pew!
CharacterSkill: Handling a gun, Horse riding, Poker
Pros: Doesn't get caught up with things and drag out their feelings
Cons: Doesn't listen to others
Hobby: Brushing her beloved horse Silver, Maintaining her guns

Name: Nara
Profile:
They call me Nara, and I'm a nun that trained quietly up on a mountain in Nishiki. 
It's a tiny thing that doesn't even compare to Mount Ooe, but there was a temple there. Oh, but now it's abandoned… but it really was a prestigious temple in its time, so...Hmmm? Oh dear, I think I should've prepared more of what I wanted to say!?
DisLike: Socializing with others, Salt (especially salt water)
CharacterSkill: Able to make her surroundings fertile and make flowers sprout
Pros: Carefree and quiet being able to calm those around her
Cons: Not the best at communicating with others

Name: Rennes
Profile:
Conductor, well met. I'm Rennes. 
I was the ranger of the Brecheliant Forest before I joined the SSS. 
My ancestors have been rangers for generations. You can rest assured I'll be a great help searching for things in the forest. 
Hyeheh, dyheheheh, how's about some galette?
DisLike: Places with lots of people, People that can't maintain a good distance
Pros: Not afraid of most conventionally scary things
Cons: Not a fan of public speaking

Name: Kuang
Profile:
Name's Kuang. I am the lighthouse keeper of Flamarine. 
I light up the ocean at night and help out the boats. 
I love heights and monkeys. 
Take me to the edge of the earth with your train, Conductor!♪
Pros: Good vision, even at night
Cons: Does things her own way

Name: Blanche
Profile:
Thanks for inviting me, sir. 
I'm Blanche. I work as a showgirl at a high class cabaret in the pleasure quarter of Verforet. 
I can promise you I'll give it my all to read the vibe of the room, so be sure to come back for another dance.
DisLike: Nothing in particular but not a fan of art
CharacterSkill: Can dance the French can-can, etc.
Pros: Able to interact with anyone without rubbing them the wrong way
Cons: Doesn't have any special feelings for others

Name: Oculus
Profile:
I'm Oculus. Don't you think all humans and creatures should be free? 
I think they should be able to go wherever whenever they want. 
So that means anythign that gets in my way, even some stupid Mist is gonna have to answer to me!
Like: New and rare things, especially fashion related
DisLike: Things that are stuck in the past
CharacterSkill: Able to determine the value of things based on the situation
Pros: Able to take action
Cons: Pretending she knows what she's talking about
Hobby: Collecting and gifting odd local souvenirs

Name: Freiburg
Profile:
Howdy! I'm Freiburg of the Eisengrad Central Army! 
I'm best at decorating trees. They even went as far as calling it tree art in the city! 
Eheheh, sure makes me blush to hear that… 
I sure hope I can meet a lot of cool friends riding with you around the world, sir!♪
Pros: Being positive and not feeling defeated
Cons: Believing people at their word
Hobby: Making things out of wood, Decorating trees

Name: King's Cross
Profile:
I'm King's Cross. A knight that's been assigned to serve one of the Chosen's family. 
I shall face any enemy that I am ordered to. 
…That sounds pretty good, doesn't it? I'm terrible at talking in front of people.
Like: Things money cannot buy and the people that chase after them
CharacterSkill: Magic, Household chores, Hairstyling, Nail art
Pros: Able to make guesses based all kinds of information
Cons: Unable to put on a fake smile, she usually doesn't say the right thing

Name: Batu
Profile:
I'm Batu. I come from a place called Skanda Cave in Flamarine. 
I've been friends with Putra since we were kids. 
But then again, I've been so busy with work with the Skanda mercenaries for the longest time. We didn't have that much time to play together. 
But anyway, I love fighting. Make sure you put me right on the front lines.
Pros: Not disliking people without a reason
Cons: Short temper, Her high pain tolerance usually results in her going overboard with things
Hobby: Appreciating and creating works of art

Name: Carthage
Profile:
I am a descendant of an ancient tribe of Verforet barbarians that terrorizes these forests. But my ancestors didn't really have much to say or leave behind,
so Idon't really know why they did what they did. So I'm relying on my teacher and all the stuff I can find at the library. I'm right in the middle of filling out all the gaps in our history.
DisLike: Dislikes (but doesn't necessarily hate) small animals
Pros: Great reflexes, Extremely intellectually curious
Cons: Tends to confuse people due to the difference in culture

Name: Tokachi
Profile:
Hello. I'm Tokachi. 
I grew up in a huuuuge, wide open field, so I'm pretty carefree, I think. 
I can use some magic and I guess I'm good at manual labor? 
Not the biggest fan of fighting, but I don't hate it. You can count me!
Pros: Excellent strength and memory
Cons: Doesn't really take action by herself if no one is ordering her

Name: Verona
Profile:
Hiiiii, I'm Verona!♪ I work as both a playwrite and an actor. 
My biggest hit was "Roberta and Julietta." It's gotten pretty famous in Verforet!♪ 
I love coming up with a good story, but I love singing and dancing oh, so much more! 
I sing all the time everywhere I go! Lalala, lahhhh!♪
Pros: Able to cheer people up with clever words
Cons: A bit over the top that people almost think she's fake
Hobby: Coming up with her original musicals and acting in it, Collecting shoes

Name: Part-Dieu
Profile:
What? Don't talk to me. Would you mind dropping dead? Ugh, I'm just so bummed out… 
So you see, I'm on the hunt for a serial killer that my sister who happens to be a detective was chasing after. I'm trying to catch them just like she was. 
Is that enough of an explanation for you? Happy now?
DisLike: Everything except her older sister, especially crime
Pros: Excellent reasoning and investigative skills
Cons: Emotionally unstable

Name: Honolulu
Profile:
I'm Honolulu! I'm the princess of the southern island! 
To put it correctly, I'm the descendant of a very curious group of people. 
They lived for hundreds of years inside a giant white whale! 
I'm skilled in ukelele, hula and surfing. What else do you wanna know? Ask me anything!
Like: Likes everything, but has recently fallen in love with coffee
Pros: Cheerful and a naturalborn leader
Cons: Has a hard time staying comfortable in one place

Name: Colombia
Profile:
Pretty mean of you to tell me you want a self-introduction. 
Well, fine then. 
As you very well know, I am Colombia, the main character of this story. 
Go ahead and laugh at me for being a braggart.
DisLike: Isn't interested in things enough to hate them
Pros: Great at anything and everything
Cons: Thinks she's being just and can quickly disturb the balance of things

Name: Shanghai
Profile:
I'm Shanghai from Eisengrad. I'm from the same town as Beijing.
We share the same taste in food too, so we are often going out to eat together. 
Probably good to point out that I'm pretty well off. 
Wh-what is that look for! You don't believe me!? 
If you keep treating me like a little kid, I won't be treating you to anything then!
Like: Beijing, Books written by Beijing, Freshwater crabs
Pros: A broad perspective, Kind to the elderly and children
Cons: Cries when overwhelmed, Tries to fix everything with money

Name: Frankfurt
Profile:
Ahem, I can't make anything like the actual frankfurts, but I'm still pretty important! 
That's cuz I'm rich! You want some money? 
Then grovel and snort like a pig for me, maybe I'll give you some pocket change? 
Come on, little piggy! Squeal for me!♪
DisLike: People that are too obidient and willingly take orders
Pros: Able to squeeze out as much money from an idea as possible
Cons: Has a hard time conveying kindness and concern for others

Name: Messina
Profile:
I joined the SSS as a medic. 
You can think of me as a doctor on the battlefield. 
I'll treat the wounds of whoever gets hurt, take them away on a stretcher… 
And deliver the coup de grace if they don't seem like they're gonna make it… 
That last bit was a joke. Just a joke us medics tell.
Like: All people that live healthily and happily
Pros: An incredibly skilled nurse
Cons: Unable to completely control her own magical artifacts

Name: Brittany
Profile:
I'm Brittany and I belon to the Verforet Military Police. 
I used to be a forest ranger in the Brecheliant Forest before joining the SSS.

Profile:
Conductor, good day.

What sort of alcohol do you like, sir?

Cons: Disappearing all of a sudden

Name: Stia
Profile:
Yo! I'm Stia and I'm from Flamarine.

Pros: Her determination

Name: Izumono Hakuto
Profile:
Boing. Boing. A-boing, boing, booooing!♪ 
 I'm Izumonohakuto and I'm the Train Knight that just loooooves anything cute.

Name: Khabarovsk
Profile:
I'm Khavarosk, a special drill instructor for the Northern Eisengrad Army. 
Pretty weird title, don't you think? Me too. 
Joining the SSS was actually the reason I went back to the Eisengrad Army. 
Guess you can say I'm pretty battle-seasoned. Sure hope you give worthwhile orders, sir.

Pros: Her fortitude
Cons: Saying immediately what comes to mind

Name: Zouérat
Profile:
*Cough, cough…* Sorry for the coughing fit. 
…I'll be fine. 
I'm, uh…really good at using golems to do heavy lifting. 
There's not really much I do for fun, but I'm game for anything.
CharacterSkill: Being able to somewhat control inorganic things
Pros: Being able to understand robot voices
Cons: Unable to open up to anyone

Name: Petropav
Profile:
Hiya. I'm Petropav. 
I run a hot spring resort way up north in the snowy mountains of Eisengrad. 
You can just call me "hostess," if you'd like!♪ 
What, why did  I decide to join the SSS, you say? 
Well, it's a long story, you know! Well, you know…
CharacterSkill: Hunting, Making stone tools, Her snow-thawing bow
Pros: Her tolerance, constant positivity and kindness
Cons: Incredibly careless

Name: Waterloo
Profile:
I'm Waterloo! I just love you, bro!♪ 
Say, where are you taking me today? 
You won't sneak out on your own, right? 
You better bring ol' Loo with ya if you go somewhere, okay?
Pros: Full of energy and always smiliing
Cons: Can't sympathize with others

Name: Blackfriar
Profile:
I'm Blackfriar, a member of the St. Iris Knights. I joined the same time that Ohana did. Part of the Zeroth Generation that formed before the SSS. 
I'm the drill instructor for all the "outsiders", so you can leave training all the newbies to me. 
I can turn any ruffian into a kitten, you just watch.
DisLike: People that want revenge, Things that don't make sense
Pros: Being patient
Cons: Particularly harsh with how she handles people close to her

Name: Akihabara
Profile:
I scrounge around for junk to repair and sell on the black market. 
That's how I make my living. I was an abandoned child myself growing up in the slums. But you know, all the people I met down there are so kind. 
I had so much fun, I love them! I'm not unhappy at all! 
There's plenty of treasures to find in a heap of junk!
Like: Families (People in red-light districts), Japanese Spaniels
Pros: Able to share her likes without any worry
Cons: Doesn't have much common sense
Hobby: Idols, Movies, Manga, The military, etc.

Name: Munich
Profile:
I'm Munich from Eisengrad. 
I believe in leading a true life with a pure heart beating in my chest. 
Hm? What are my hobbies? I don't really have any. 
If I had to say, I'd say walking around is one… But I guess you can't call that a hobby.
CharacterSkill: Guessing what's in food with a blindfold on
Pros: Being able to risk her life for strangers
Cons: Being inflexible, Often jumps to conclusions

Name: Ayala
Profile:
Fiiiiiish on! I'm Ayala! 
I just love the ocean! And boats! 
If there's anything you wanna know about me, just ask, okay? 
Huh? What's my best school subject? I don't have one! I'm horrible at studying!
Pros: Wits of steel
Cons: Unable to match people's pace

Name: Port Royal
Profile:
I'm Port Royal, captain of a pirate crew so fearsome even a crying babe would silence itself. 
I've sailed the 7 seas, stealing countless treasures--I don't let anything go once I have it in my sights! 
Call me a ruthless, inhuman savage of the sea! 
You all better tremble in fear when I raise my flag! Wahahah!
CharacterSkill: Sailing, Fighting in places with poor footing
Pros: Not worrying about small details
Cons: Unable to follow the rules
Hobby: Being able to act like a pirate

Name: Austerlitz
Profile:
How do you do, Conductor? I'm part of the Verforet Military Police, Austerlitz. 
I grew up deep in the dimly lit forest surrounded by stacks of books. 
Therefore my social skills are a bit lacking, but I'm a good match for Rennes. 
We both get all nervous and have no idea what we're saying. 
Well anyway, that was my introduction.
Like: Creative works depicting love between men and women (18+)
DisLike: Large gatherings of people like parties
CharacterSkill: Magic to see long distances, speed reading
Pros: Her ability to focus
Cons: Cannot honestly speak her mind

Name: Costa Rica
Profile:
I'm an shrine maiden sworn to protect the seas and lands of Flamarine. 
I helped set up the barrier at the Underwater Temple. 
They liked me for my skills so much that they employed me as the chairperson to open the summits at the temple. 
Though I have now left the position for a myriad of reasons.
CharacterSkill: Ancient Flamarine magic, Raising plants and animals
Pros: Full of mercy and compassion
Cons: Morbidly overprotective

Name: Kinugawa
Profile:
Greetings, I'm Kinugawa. I'm part of the Tsukiyo Banshuu, a special spy force for the Nishiki Army. 
Before I joined the SSS I would work alongside my happy-go-lucky apprentice Nikkou. 
We would go on all kinds of important missions. 
I'll carry out whatever you ask of me for work, but please nothing more than that, okay? 
I'm not much for troublesome chores.
Like: Nishiki arms such as swords and armor
CharacterSkill: All household chores like cooking and laundry
Pros: Her tenacity, she doesn't give up halfway through
Cons: Lacking in enthusiasm

Name: Nikko
Profile:
Hi, Conductor! I'm Nikkou! I'm from Nishiki! So happy! 
I worked real hard training so I could finally join the Tsukiyo Banshuu! 
I'm gonna work even harder with my master as part of the SSS! Thanks again for letting me join!
Like: The tragic tale of the war god Shibazakura
CharacterSkill: Distinguishing weapons and armor apart by their smell
Pros: Able to be kind to anyone
Cons: Acting dumb

Name: Khajuraho
Profile:
I'm a monk from a peculiar temple in the backcountry of Flamarine. 
I was the animal trainer there. 
It was my job to remold these beasts without any understanding of people into those with some smarts… Heheh♪ 
Would you want to see how I'd train you, sir?
Pros: Mentally tough
Cons: Pointing out other's shortcomings

Name: Pleven
Profile:
I'm the last survivor of a small kingdom that was taken by the Phantom Mist. 
After my mother did all she could to save me, I was educated as a gifted individual to become the fighting machine I am today. 
And here you have my selfless devotion to realize the ideal kingdom we all deserve.
Pros: Obedience
Cons: Lack of self

Name: Grenoble
Profile:
How do I even… You want me to introduce myself? That's tough… 
I've lived over two hundred years at this point. Led quite a tumultuous life and I really can't sum it up in a few words.

Like: Alcohol, Tobacco, Gambling, Precious metals, Money
Pros: Many real-world experiences
Cons: Pessimistic, A sucker for cheap thrills

Name: Wernigerode
Profile:
I'm Wernigerode, a magician from the Harz mountain range in Eisengrad. 
A magician, not a witch, okay, Conductor? 
Harz magic wasn't taking the battlefield into account. 
It's for the purpose of dreams and hopes and smiles. I await the day that I can show it to you first hand.
Pros: A strong sense of responsibility
Cons: Doesn't doubt what others say

Name: Fontaine
Profile:
I'm Fontaine, part of the Verforet Military Police. 
Before joining the SSS, I worked as a ranger in Brecheliant. 
I come from a petite tribe called Shana and am pretty weak myself. 
But even still, I always dreamed of being like Rennes and Brittany. 
Probably doesn't mean much coming from me, but I worked myself to the bone to get here.

Like: Gathering around the dining table with gusto for dinner parties, etc.
CharacterSkill: Listening to the heartbeats of trees and things
Pros: Positivity when it comes to facing difficult things
Cons: Inflexible

Name: Bestyakh
Profile:
I'm Bestyakh of the Northern Eisengrad Army. 
I thought I couldn't go back into the service, but my sister pulled some strings so I could. 
Well, now I'm here with the SSS, so I'll be with her a bit longer. 
I'm pretty knowledgable about the Mist and ancient machines, just so you know. 
It's a pleasure to work with you.
CharacterSkill: Putting together machines and making blueprints, Making candy
Pros: Spares no effort when it comes to achieving a goal
Cons: Selfish

Name: Karamachi
Profile:
Hiya, I'm Karamachi, a shopkeep.

I'm not the biggest fan of fighting, but I'll do my best to help you all out.
Pros: Open-minded about everything
Cons: Indecisive

Name: Shiyan
Profile:
I'm Shiyan. I belong to the Central Eisengrad Army.

I'm a martial artist raised in the Wudang mountains. 
I'm always itching to fight someone stronger than me. 
I'll take anyone on that wants to spar, so don't hesitate to ask!
Pros: Unafraid of strong enemies, Doesn't lie
Cons: Lacking in common sense
Hobby: Training, Reading manga that Beijing recommends

Race: 人間と霜の鬼神のハーフ

Name: 相州蛇子
Profile: 五車学園の学生対魔忍、相州蛇子だよ～。車掌ちゃん、よろしくね。/n蛇子、ふうまちゃんと一緒に『独立遊撃隊』をやってるんだ。/n私の忍術は『獣遁の術』。この特鉄隊でだって、タコ足とタコ墨を使っていっぱい活躍しちゃうんだから。
Pros: タコができる事全部
Cons: 魚臭い墨を吐く

Name: 井河アサギ
Profile: 五車学園の校長を務めさせてもらっている。/n最強の対魔忍などと言われることもあるが、私もまだ道の途中。これからも魔を滅するため戦うだけよ。
Pros: どんな状況に陥っても生存を諦めない胆力
Cons: 情を捨てきれない

Name: カオヤイ
Profile: Mフレイマリンのカオヤイだよ～。/n自然と動物が大好きな女の子。え？　言わなくてもそれはわかるって？/nそうだよね。動物の紹介じゃあないんだもんね。/n自己紹介って難しいなぁ。あたし、自分の紹介って一番ニガテかも～。
DisLike: 武器、兵器、自然破壊につながるもの
CharacterSkill: 動物と心を通わすこと、森林でのサバイバル
Pros: 人や動物に優しい、滅多なことでは怒らない
Cons: 勉強ができない

Name: アディスアベバ
Profile: 貴様に謎々を出すわ、世界で最も優れた人種は何？/n当然、ダークエルフよね。/nあたしの故郷は人類発祥の地で、そこで暮らす人間はすべてダークエルフよ。/nあたしたちこそが、最も純粋で偉大な『人間』というわけよ。
Like: ダークエルフ、謎かけ、辛い料理、チャットの葉
DisLike: ダークエルフ以外の人種、毛深い生き物、異文化
CharacterSkill: 『秘宝』を用いて様々な奇跡が起こせる
Pros: 自分が「正しい」と思ったものは全力で愛し、肯定する
Cons: 自分が間違っていると絶対に認めない
Hobby: 自国や己の文化の偉大さを説くこと

Name: ツルガオカ
Profile: 本来は他言無用にござりますが、亭主さまにはお話しいたしましょう。/nわたくしめはＭニシキの暗部、『闇夜の烏』と仮称される暗殺組織の人間でござります。/n地上では忍者、と呼ぶのでしょうか、あの方々と同じようなものと思っていただいて構いませぬが――/nより穢らわしく忌み嫌われる、汚れ仕事を請け負っております。
Like: 家事、反物、銀杏、亭主、恩返し
DisLike: 恩知らず、露出、現代的な娯楽
CharacterSkill: 己の羽根で紡いだ糸を用いた反物作り
Pros: 家事全般（特に機織り）が得意
Cons: 現代的な価値観・倫理観について無知
Hobby: 亭主のために身を尽くすこと

Name: バラブー
Profile: ブーちゃんはね～、地上でいちばん有名だった『史上最高のサーカス』団の団員だったんだよ～！/nだから、サーカスならではの芸は一通り見せられるかな～？　何が見たい～？/nおどけてふざけて歌って踊って、あなたを笑顔にしてみせるよ～！　ぶひぶひっ♪
Like: 笑顔、サーカス、各種の芸、ファン
DisLike: 動物、獣人、負の感情、火災
CharacterSkill: 動物芸以外のサーカスっぽい曲芸
Pros: 常に明るくあっけらかんとしている
Cons: 空気が読めない
Hobby: 芸を見せて、喜んでもらうこと

Name: オアハカ
Profile: こんにちは。Ｍフレイマリンから来ましたオアハカです。/n亡くなった人の霊と交流することができます。/nでも、自分の家族とだけは話すことができないんですよ。不思議ですよね。
CharacterSkill: 霊界との交流（自分の親族とは交流できない）
Pros: 人（生死問わず）の話に耳を傾けること
Cons: 都合が悪いときは母親との会話に逃避してしまうこと

Name: エトルタ
Profile: デカ長にだけはこっそり教えますが、自分は全員が何らかの犯罪者という変な一族の末裔です。自分の場合は盗みの才能があって、地元では伝説の『怪盗淑女ル・アーヴル』の再来と言われてました！/nでも大丈夫ですよっ、今は改心してますから！　自分は真面目な捜査官でありマス！
Like: 故郷の景色、抽象画などの芸術品、頭の良いひと
CharacterSkill: どんなに厳重な警備もすり抜けて目当てのものを盗める
Pros: 怪盗としては超一流、善良
Cons: 優柔不断、捜査官としてかなり無能
Hobby: 故郷の景色や芸術品を眺めること、怪盗ごっこ

Name: ベリガン
Profile: Mフレイマリン鉄道軍のベリガンです。/n森林を火災から守る森林消防隊にも所属しています。/nもちろん、居住区で火災が発生した際にも駆けつけますよ。/n体力には自信があるので、体を使う仕事は任せてください
Pros: 困ってる人に積極的に手を差し伸べるところ
Cons: アツくなりすぎるところ

Name: クマモト
Profile: クマモトです。Mニシキ鉄道軍に所属しています。/nクマは、呪術師のミヤコさんのことをとても尊敬しています。/nクマも、ミヤコさんのようにかっこよくなりたい。堂々と戦えるようになりたい。/n車掌さま、クマに、くーるな戦い方を教えてくださいね？
Like: 堂々としている人、辛子蓮根
DisLike: たくさん話しかけてくる人
Pros: 力が強いところ、ガマン強いところ
Cons: 自分の意見がハッキリ言えないところ

Name: カターニア
Profile: アァ……。私、かたぁにぁ……。オ願イダカラ、私ニ近ヅカナイデ……。/n私、触ッタ人ヲ殺シチャウノ……。毒？　毒ガ、出テルノカモ？/nダカラ、オ願イダカラ私ニ関ワラナイデ……。私、貴方ヲ殺シタクナイノ。
Like: 植物（特にブラッドオレンジ）、清らかな空気と水
DisLike: 暴言・暴力、穢れ、火、動物
CharacterSkill: 植物を操ることができる
Pros: 純粋無垢で善良
Cons: 穢れに弱すぎる
Hobby: 植物の世話、消毒、パンの生地をこねること

Name: イソベ
Profile: おらはＭニシキ国内における最後の秘境、とか言われてる『群魔圏（ぐんまけん）』出身なんさ。/nおら自身はべつに大したことない、むしろ普通より役立たずの穀潰しだけども……。ごはんさえ食べさせてもらえるなら、おら、あんたのために一生懸命がんばるつもりだべ♪
Like: お米、湯豆腐、民話、俳句、正直者、踊り
CharacterSkill: ニシキの古代語が読める
Pros: どれだけ失敗しても踏んづけられてもめげない。タフ。
Cons: 学習能力がない
Hobby: 民話の収集、温泉巡り、盗み食い

Name: メアリー
Profile: セントイリス騎士団所属のメアリー・ローズガーデンよ。/nいろいろあって長いこと霧の中を彷徨っていた……ということになっているの。/nまあ、あなたには多くを語る必要はないわよね。/n戦いは任せて。剣の腕には自信があるわ。これでも一応、元騎士団長だからね。
Like: バラの花に関するもの
Pros: 芯が通っていること
Cons: やや短気なところ

Name: ユウゼン
Profile: ユウゼンだよ。いちおうニシキ軍に所属したってことになるのかね。/n軍服なんて飾りだよ。あたしは自分の目的のために生きるんだ。/n初代ユウゼンの作品を探す。特鉄隊を手伝うのはそのついでさ。/nあんたの命令なんて聞かないからね。そこんとこ、忘れるんじゃないよ。
DisLike: お人形をぞんざいに扱う人、馴れ馴れしい人
Pros: 我慢強く、度胸がある
Cons: 人とあまり仲良くしようとしない

Name: Dr.グローリア
Profile: えっ、自己紹介ですの？ まぁ必要ですの、お互いのこと何も知りませんものね？/nどくたぁは、えぇっとドッガン団の首領で、その前はお母ちゃまに――うう～？/nと、とりあえず、『お兄ちゃまのことが大好き！』ってことだけ知っていてもらえれば充分ですの♪
DisLike: 毛虫、興味のない分野のお勉強、苦い食べ物
Pros: 天才であること、良い子であること
Cons: 天才なのにアホであること、悪役なのに良い子であること

Name: パレルモ
Profile: 私は古王国シティリアの偉大なる錬金術によって生まれた、人造人間（ホムンクルス）よ。/n今では古王国は濃い幻霧に呑まれて近づくこともできないけど、いつか絶対に取り返してやるわ。/nそのために、私は『正義の医院長』として日夜、戦っているの。
Like: 錬金術、ジェラート、規則を守ること
DisLike: 病、セクハラ、反社会的な存在
Pros: 真面目で努力家
Cons: 些細な違反も許せない、常に自分が正しいと思っている
Hobby: 悪党退治、ジェラート店巡り、錬金術の実験、水浴び

Name: クヴェトリンブルク
Profile: ハルツ魔法アカデミーから来ましたクヴェトリンブルクです。/nヴェルニゲローデとはアカデミーの同級生で、小さいころからずっと友達なんですよ。/nわたしはハルツには珍しいタイプの魔法使いで、攻撃魔法が得意です。ゴスラー先生と一緒ですね。/nみんなの笑顔のために、わたしも戦います。車掌さん、これからよろしくお願いします。
Like: 魔法を題材にした物語
Pros: 頑張りやさん
Cons: 好きなことに熱中すると周りが見えなくなる
Hobby: 物語を書くこと、マンガを読むこと

Name: オシアゲ
Profile: あたしは氏も素性も定かじゃない、単なるゴロつきだからね。/n右も左もわかんない餓鬼のころに、岡場所の連中に拾われて育てられたのサ。/nな～んて昔のことはスコンと忘れて、今は鳶職として気ままなその日暮らしをしてるよ。
Like: 高いところ、建築、祭、花火、義理人情
DisLike: 粋じゃないこと、岡場所の仕事、「今」以外を考えること
Pros: 義理人情に厚くて世話好き、頼れる姉御肌
Cons: 大雑把、けっこう頑固
Hobby: 角・槍・建物の手入れ

Name: ハチロク
Profile: わたくしは旧帝鉄8620形蒸気機関車トップナンバー機8620の/n専用レイルロオド、ハチロクと申します。/n車掌様と共に世界の安心を守るために――/nセントイリス発、定時。出発！　進行です！
Pros: 礼儀作法に通じている。言葉遣いが綺麗
Cons: プライドが高すぎ、メンタルに脆いところがある

Name: オリヴィ
Profile: 冥国製の汎用型レイルロオド、オリヴィだよっ！/n元みかん鉄道――今は御一夜鉄道でⅨ号機関車を走らせてるんだ。/n列車の安全はオリヴィがしっかり守ってみせるよ。それじゃ、出発進行～！
Like: ムナカタ、ヤツシロカイの夕陽
CharacterSkill: 職務経験豊富で保線に関する造詣も深い
Pros: 明るく前向き、コミュ力が高い
Cons: 我慢しすぎる。自身の出自へのコンプレックス

Name: れいな
Profile: レイルロオドのれいなといいますぅ。/n御一夜鉄道で、社長のポーレットといっしょに、/nキハ07sを走らせてるんですよぉ。/nイリスクラウドでも、元気に安全運行でがんばりますねぇ。
Like: ポーレット、世界の全て
CharacterSkill: 動物や赤子と心通わすことが出来る
Pros: 誰をも愛し、誰からも愛される
Cons: 居眠り癖

Name: ニイロク
Profile: 自分はクハ26専用レイルロオド、ニイロク。/n試験運転士・赤井清春と組み、日々テストを続けていた。/nでも。帝鉄が解体され、計画は闇に葬られた。/n残ったのは、この小さな運転体だけ。それでも、自分はまだここにいる。
Pros: 最新鋭機なので性能が非常に高い
Cons: 深刻な故障により表情が一切変化しない

Name: ひよこ
Profile: 旧帝鉄C57、145専用レイルロオド。/n旺宮鉄道歴史館の実質的な館長を勤めております。/n不死鳥博士とでも呼んでいただけると幸いですな。
Like: 安芸（電車姫）、旺宮鉄道歴史館
CharacterSkill: レイルロオドのメンテナンス
Pros: 鉄道に関する、広範で深淵な知識を有する
Cons: ついつい他者をテストしてしまう

Name: スィーリア
Profile: 私は、スィーリア・クマーニ・エイントリー。/nジョストの名門校であるウィンフォード学園の生徒会長を務めている。/n君もジョストに興味があるようだな。馬上で相まみえるのが楽しみだ。
Like: グヤーシュ(シチュー)、お好み焼き
Pros: あらゆる面で完璧、誰にでも分け隔てなく接する
Cons: ややプライドが高い、人を頼らない、世間とズレている
Hobby: クマのぬいぐるみ集め、お風呂

Name: 希咲美桜
Profile: 自己紹介、ですか？　了解です！　希咲美桜、ウィンフォード学園普通科です。/nはい、騎士科やベグライター科じゃないんですよ。でも、ジョストを愛する気持ちはみんなと同じです！/nここでも、ジョストが好きな友だちをたくさん増やせたらいいな～。
Like: ティータイム、創作料理(美味しくない）
Pros: おっとりしているが芯が強い
Cons: 少しうっかりしたところがある
Hobby: お茶の葉集め、消しゴムはんこ

Name: 龍造寺茜
Profile: ウィンフォード学園、騎士科の龍造寺茜だ。/n幼少の頃から鍛え上げた剣の技術を活かせば、ジョストにおいて、この世界での戦いにおいて、誰よりも抜きんでる自信がある。/nただひとり、憧れのスィーリア先輩を除いてはな。
Like: 五月、スイーツ、朝の剣道の練習、天ぷら
Pros: 真面目で負けん気が強く、しっかり者
Cons: 寂しがり屋
Hobby: スイーツのお店の発掘、ファッション誌の熟読

Name: 大蔵りそな
Profile: どうも、大蔵りそなです。/n兄達と一緒にこの世界にやって来たのですが、何分私はヒッキーのネトオタなので、ぶっちゃけちょっと緊張してます。/n役に立てるかわかりませんが、兄共々どうぞよろしくお願いします。
Pros: 実は成績優秀
Cons: 人付き合いが苦手

Name: 桜小路ルナ
Profile: 私は桜小路ルナだ。フィリア女学院で服飾を学んでいる。/n君は私の容貌を目にしても、驚かないのか？/nそうか、ならば合格だ。メイドとしてではなく、頼れるリーダーとして君のことを認めよう。
Like: 朝日(恋人)、遊星(夫)、八千代
Pros: 努力を努力と思わない
Cons: 苦手なものを放置しがち

Name: 柳ヶ瀬湊
Profile: 初めまして。柳ヶ瀬湊っていいます。/n実家は運送会社です！　力仕事は得意です！/n昔から男勝りでおてんばって言われるんですけど、初恋の人に可愛いって思われたくて……。/nちなみに、まだ初恋継続中……って朝日！　何こっそり聞いてんだあ！
Pros: ポジティブ、明るい
Cons: 大雑把

Name: マキ
Profile: 我が名はマキ。鬼人ヶ城の城主。オオエ山の守人の一人。/n初代シモアマヅの弟子。誇り高き鬼人。/n己の信念を曲げず、故郷を忘れず、人を愛し、人のために戦う。
CharacterSkill: アクセサリーなどの小物を作ること
Pros: 嘘をつかないこと
Cons: 頑固なところ

Name: プウネネ
Profile: ネネさまは『白鯨』のお腹のなかにあった小国家で、『女神』として信仰されてたですよ。/n今は色々あってＭセントイリスでパティシエとして働いてるですが、何もないところから無限にお砂糖を生成する、という奇跡を起こせるです！ えへんえへん♪
Like: 砂糖、お菓子作り、太ったひと、水泳
DisLike: 飢餓、ダイエット、クジラを嫌うひと
CharacterSkill: 砂糖を無限に生成でき、それで美味しいお菓子がつくれる
Pros: 苦しんでいるひとを無償で救おうとするところ
Cons: 他人を太らせようとする、あんまり人の話を聞かない
Hobby: みんなにお菓子を振る舞うこと
